                    "value": "<p>The immolis targets a living creature within 30 feet and directs a beam of volatile psychic energy toward it, increasing the rate at which the creature's body produces heat. The target must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:20] save. The second and third time an immolis uses Heat Beam in the same round, the DC lowers to @Check[type:fortitude|dc:16] or @Check[type:fortitude|dc:16], respectively.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes [[/r (2d6+5)[fire]]].</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes [[/r (4d6+5)[fire]]] and [[/r 5[persistent,fire]]] damage.</p>"
